msgid "Get mini-cart data"
msgstr "取得迷你購物車資料"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Retrieve the current cart contents formatted for the mini-cart "
"component.\n"
"\n"
"    Works for both authenticated users (cart linked to user account) and\n"
"    anonymous users (cart linked to session). Cart data includes all items\n"
"    with product details, quantities, prices, and images.\n"
"\n"
"    **Use Cases:**\n"
"    - Initial mini-cart load on page\n"
"    - Refreshing cart after external changes\n"
"    - Checking cart status before checkout\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** None required (uses session for anonymous users)\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    取得目前購物車內容，格式化為迷你購物車組件使用。支援已驗證用戶（購物車與"
"用戶賬戶連結）和匿名用戶（購物車與會話連結）。購物車資料包括所有商品的詳細資"
"訊、數量、價格和圖片。**使用場景：** - 頁面初始迷你購物車載入 - 在外部更改後"
"重新整理購物車 - 下單前檢查購物車狀態 **驗證：** 不需要驗證（對匿名用戶使用會"
"話）\n"
"    "

msgid "Cart data retrieved successfully"
msgstr "購物車資料已成功取得"

msgid "Update cart item quantity"
msgstr "更新購物車項目數量"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Update the quantity of an item in the cart.\n"
"\n"
"    Set quantity to 0 to remove the item entirely. The endpoint validates\n"
"    stock availability before updating and returns the full updated cart.\n"
"\n"
"    **Use Cases:**\n"
"    - Increment/decrement quantity buttons in mini-cart\n"
"    - Direct quantity input changes\n"
"    - Removing items (quantity=0)\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** None required (validates item belongs to user's "
"cart)\n"
"\n"
"    **Validation:**\n"
"    - Item must exist in user's cart\n"
"    - Quantity must be non-negative integer\n"
"    - Stock availability is checked for inventory-tracked products\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    更新購物車中商品的數量。將數量設為 0 可完全移除該商品。此端點在更新前會驗"
"證庫存可用性，並返回完整的更新後購物車。**使用場景：** - 迷你購物車中的增加/"
"減少數量按鈕 - 直接輸入數量更改 - 移除商品（數量=0） **驗證：** 不需要驗證"
"（驗證商品是否屬於用戶的購物車） **驗證條件：** - 商品必須存在於用戶的購物車"
"中 - 數量必須是非負整數 - 對於庫存追蹤商品會檢查庫存可用性\n"
"    "

msgid "Cart updated successfully"
msgstr "購物車已成功更新"

msgid "Invalid request data or insufficient stock"
msgstr "請求資料無效或庫存不足"

msgid "Cart item not found"
msgstr "未找到購物車項目"

msgid "Remove item from cart"
msgstr "從購物車移除項目"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Remove an item from the cart entirely.\n"
"\n"
"    Returns the updated cart data after removal.\n"
"\n"
"    **Use Cases:**\n"
"    - Delete button on cart items\n"
"    - Clearing specific items\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** None required (validates item belongs to user's "
"cart)\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    從購物車中完全移除一個項目。移除後會返回更新後的購物車資料。**使用案例："
"** - 購物車項目上的刪除按鈕 - 清除特定項目 **認證：** 不需要（會驗證項目是否"
"屬於用戶的購物車）\n"
"    "

msgid "Item removed successfully"
msgstr "項目已成功移除"

msgid "Get empty cart recommendations"
msgstr "取得空購物車推薦"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get intelligent product recommendations for the empty cart state.\n"
"\n"
"    Returns personalized suggestions organized into labeled sections based "
"on:\n"
"    - **Recently viewed**: Products the user has browsed (session-based for "
"anonymous users)\n"
"    - **Related**: Products in the same categories as recently viewed items\n"
"    - **On sale**: Currently discounted products\n"
"    - **Trending**: Popular products by views/sales\n"
"    - **Featured**: Editor-picked products as fallback\n"
"\n"
"    All returned products are verified to be in stock and available for "
"purchase.\n"
"\n"
"    **Use Cases:**\n"
"    - Empty cart state in mini-cart\n"
"    - \"You might like\" sections\n"
"    - Cross-sell opportunities\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** None required (uses session for anonymous users)\n"
"\n"
"    **Personalization:**\n"
"    - Anonymous users: Based on session recently-viewed products\n"
"    - Authenticated users: Based on account history and preferences\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    為空購物車狀態提供智能產品推薦。返回根據以下條件組織的個人化建議，分為標"
"籤分區：- **最近瀏覽**：用戶瀏覽過的產品（對匿名用戶為會話基礎）- **相關產品"
"**：與最近瀏覽過的產品位於相同類別的產品- **正在銷售**：目前有折扣的產品- **"
"熱門產品**：根據瀏覽次數/銷售量的熱門產品- **特色產品**：編輯精選的產品作為備"
"用所有返回的產品均經確認有庫存且可供購買。**使用場景**：- 小型購物車中的空購"
"物車狀態- \"您可能喜歡\" 分區- 跨賣機會**驗證**：不需要驗證（對匿名用戶使用會"
"話）**個人化**：- 匿名用戶：根據會話中最近瀏覽過的產品- 已驗證用戶：根據賬戶"
"歷史記錄和偏好\n"
"    "

